{"tid":150322,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"發起罷食麥當勞","createTime":"2017-03-10T02:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T06:40:18.000Z","uid":54736,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70a091d8121e64a7f0927303a18c2fb0047e844e","tid":150322,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"講真你加新包咪加囉，點解要取消舊包？<br />\n你取消嘅仲要係多人食嘅包。<br />\n<br />\n呢家出啲懶高級嘅包咪盞冇人幫襯你？唔好唔記得幫襯你嘅好多都係學生哥，窮撚咋！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 罷食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 助長繼續取消舊包"},{"pid":"20ed978a2f7a82793466cc9d452d66d45b74cc52","tid":150322,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"冇食好耐, 年紀開始大, M記野食對我黎講比較熱氣, <br />\n<br />\n食完感覺會唔係幾好"},{"pid":"c75c05783a9290ce7f1497338ad80e3790c54889","tid":150322,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇食好耐, 年紀開始大, M記野食對我黎講比較熱氣, <br />\n<br />\n食完感覺會唔係幾好</blockquote><br />\n其實感覺上板雞或者啲冇炸嘅包冇咁熱氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (我認自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"0a19c45e40f9027dfbca89e688444b7b869e152a","tid":150322,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"竟然有人支持取消舊包<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be102a53f679734acac7a359afbc37c87582ff23","tid":150322,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"變做中資就應該要唔食啦，理得佢轉咩包"},{"pid":"8ffcf1898d543dceaf9976c38dff6f697a014343","tid":150322,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然有人支持取消舊包<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又唔食m記既，佢最好乜柒都取消之後執柒左去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667af223441e4fa5ed5b99e391053d192a65187c","tid":150322,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:53:42.000Z","msg":"55波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b235b4eb637cf8ca0fd11f2cfd834e08ac959a5c","tid":150322,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>變做中資就應該要唔食啦，理得佢轉咩包</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a26f959cadc5f11a4572c0fdd83ce2e0d73b417","tid":150322,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>竟然有人支持取消舊包<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又唔食m記既，佢最好乜柒都取消之後執柒左去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔食，理得佢執唔執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb6f28825f3e5171da9ef8bf0f18f626361a7a9","tid":150322,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"on9港豬成日話罷食麥當勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea2f17571f8681f8702a8ab95f45a365cf1ca84","tid":150322,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:58:17.000Z","msg":"不了 仲要脆香雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e378e09a2b53224eb3505fd02fc1c336c150b8ec","tid":150322,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"不了 仲要食脆香雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im